===============================================================================
Linux SUSIIoT Library
===============================================================================

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
How to install/uninstall SUSIIoT Library & run demo AP
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
install
        1) Extract the gzip file.
           user$ tar zxf SUSIIoT_Release.gz
        2) Execute install.sh and Press 1 to install SUSIIoT.
           user# sudo ./release/library/install.sh 
        3) Execute demo AP.
           user# sudo ./release/sampleCode/demo/output/SusiiotDemo
		   
uninstall
        1) Execute install.sh and Press 2 to uninstall SUSIIoT.
           user# sudo ./release/library/install.sh 

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Compile Sample Sources AP
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
        1) main.cpp is the sample source code.
        2) Make sure libSusiIoT.so and libjansson.so in your library/ folder.
        3) Refer to "Makefile", then use "make" to compile it.
		
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Folder explanation
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
        1) release/library/
           SUSIIoT essential libraries and module libraries
        2) reease/sampleCode/demo
           SUSIIoT demo AP
        3) release/sampleCode/IoTJsonLibrary
           SUSI_IOT_API for SUSI_IOT Json format.
        4) release/sampleCode/SampleLib
           For integrating sensor data from external sensors 
        
           
